    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You aren’t as easy to hit when surrounded.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Perception 3 ranks</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to KAC against attacks from foes that flank you. If either foe has a CR that’s equal to or higher than your level, you don’t gain this bonus.</p>\n<p><strong>Teamwork Benefit:</strong> If you’re adjacent to an ally who also has this feat, you instead gain a +2 circumstance bonus to KAC against attacks from foes that flank you, and you gain this bonus no matter the CR of your opponents.</p>\n<p><em>Enable/Disable additional KAC bonus in the Modifiers tab.</em></p>"
    },
